voxtty (0.1.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix Command mode tool calling (process_command wrapper handling)
  * Add systemd user service for auto-start on boot
  * Enable systemctl --user control (start/stop/restart/status)
  * Service reads from user config (~/.config/voxtty/config.toml)
  * Add text output toggle to tray menu (like TUI 'o' key)
  * Add Command mode to tray mode selection menu
  * Service runs with realtime ElevenLabs mode and bidirectional by default
  * Default backend set to ElevenLabs realtime

 -- Jeff Laflamme <meetjeff@pm.me>  Sat, 28 Dec 2024 08:15:00 +0000

voxtty (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Voice-controlled assistant with wake-word mode switching
  * AI assistant, code, and dictation modes
  * Real-time speech-to-text conversion with VAD
  * System tray icon with toggle control
  * System-wide typing via ydotool
  * Support for local Whisper and cloud AI backends
  * Realtime WebSocket streaming (~150ms latency)
  * Echo test mode for audio verification
  * Interactive device and model selection

 -- Jeff Laflamme <meetjeff@pm.me>  Wed, 15 Oct 2025 15:00:00 +0000
